summary: An Ordinance repealing Ordinance No. 7345, entitled "An Ordinance providing for the improvement of East Olive Street, in the City of Seattle, be improved from Thirty-seventh Avenue to Lake Washington, by grading and parking the same, and providing for the payment therefor by the mode of "Immediate Payment," under the provisions of Ordinance No. 5693 of said city, approved December 6, 1899."
